title: #126: Bag Man (@CortMcCown)
itunes:title: Bag Man with Cort McCown
description: Cort McCown came over to my LA apartment before I left for New York and we talked about his sweet ass job as a professional caddy on the PGA tour. It's the golf equivalent to being a ball boy. But way cooler than that because you get to make money and you're a grown man now.
